  "description": "Osprey's ShoreSystem amplitude envelope breathes directly into Overdub's tape mix, sculpting the reverb character with each tidal surge. The coastline is the dub engine — high-water moments bloom into long echo trails; retreating tides pull the signal back to dry. An oceanic dub machine.",
